dataStore.get: List all data stored in the API. Could be a lot of data.

fishes.get: List all the fishes ever spawned, regardless of their current status, and with their default spawn characteristics.
fishes.put: Create a new fish. The response will return the fish that has just been created. Note that more ticks will also be created to fill in all the gaps until the created fish spawns.

ticks.get: List all the ticks ever created.
ticks.put: Create a new tick by incrementing from highest tick to the next one.
